sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser
    participant W as Web server
    participant C as Controller

    B->>W: GET /nodes/{id}

    rect rgb(240, 232, 255)
        Note over W,C: fan-out in parallel<br/>(one system API key + X-On-Behalf-Of)
        W->>C: GET /api/v1/nodes/{id}
        W->>C: GET /api/v1/agents/{id}
        W->>C: GET /api/v1/nodes/{id}/containers
        W->>C: GET /api/v1/events?subject=node:...
        C-->>W: node data
        C-->>W: agent data
        C-->>W: container list
        C-->>W: recent events
    end

    Note over W: maud templates compose<br/>responses into HTML fragment
    W-->>B: rendered page (one round-trip)
